清問楚，係咪真係唔會超左LIMTED之後就限速,咁我信鳩佢，續撚左約。<br />\n前排用超左LIMITED,打機睇片慢撚到仆街,之後度一度速度,屌你老尾真係限速,跟住我打去嘈,叫佢抽返錄音俾我聽,佢就淨係播返個SALES用急口令速度速返合約條文果段俾我聽,原來果段條文係話「用超過LIMTED後,唔會限速,但會因應當時區域使用量而排序優先次序」，屌啦星咁即係限速啦，咁仲點實現佢講果句＂真無限＂，又俾佢水撚左，當買個教訓，含家產！"},{"pid":"2396525ea59ec5c23489a763e1fd2946006226c6","tid":1770500,"uid":219718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a549c1e729db33d28f6d2c07f221d19815c21f2","tid":1770500,"uid":88304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:48:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d4b1a1016033541d9d9214b0522bd05ebef5314","tid":1770500,"uid":219718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:07:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c83257660227814a987b560ce97a25eb254ff19","tid":1770500,"uid":251818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:50:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d358426c3d0a32ecc5f054e25be75c1c34a3d1e7","tid":1770500,"uid":88304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:17:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"182a801e3ab1ee2a2db763fe25a7eb19dc4b73b1","tid":1770500,"uid":219718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:52:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d14c3714e4e997cddcf7729ae961a328ed4e20ff","tid":1770500,"uid":342056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:12:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"826cba5a1b51c76ab4ddbc01da3e5cc3f9059717","tid":1770500,"uid":88304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:17:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8057d8c290153ba86d2340ed675565b29529325d","tid":1770500,"uid":219718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T06:22:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6957df56784cf530a336bc9c2ac683b8c7ad6c7","tid":1770500,"uid":219718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:57:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3d2e1f6b93096b